# sdist contents for buddhi-review.
#
# The test tree is development-only: it ships in neither the wheel nor a normal
# install, and its `conftest.py` (the gh/model seam shims) is not packaged, so a
# bundled `pytest` could not run anyway. Prune it from the sdist so the published
# tarball matches the already-clean wheel (one source surface for users, no stray
# fixture files). Run the suite from a clone: `pip install -e ".[test]"`.
prune tests
